{"tid":1386353,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唉，你地做咩咁驚水炮車？","createTime":"2019-07-30T10:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T08:49:48.000Z","uid":13759,"like":490,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"7e654dae936f31487721df94f9906dfc639a1b56","tid":1386353,"uid":13759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:24:27.000Z","msg":"講好咗Hit and Run啦，無人叫你企係度俾人射，佢黎到咪即刻散水坐車去另一區再示威過囉。<br />\n<br />\n最簡單對付警察同水炮車既方法，就係當佢要走果陣就立即走，打遊擊，諗方法對付佢做咩？打機打上腦？<br />\n<br />\n根本就無得打+無需要打。各位諗清楚我地行動目標係咩，目標就係賭香港經濟同前途去換取五大訴求！<br />\n<br />\n得罪講，你俾水炮射死政府都唔在乎，做咩要送頭？重諗點對付警察？<br />\n<br />\nBe water呀，講咗咁撚耐都唔撚係Be water。你企定定俾人射點Be Water呀！！！"},{"pid":"43796b5b9541b16ea9f2c2f89f973b213512a418","tid":1386353,"uid":263161,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:27:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"135cf6abf23018b2b68895c1a81814696fe6baa3","tid":1386353,"uid":13759,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:28:00.000Z","msg":"架車黎，警察唔會即刻開炮架啦，即刻散，再集合，你坐地鐵走快定佢水炮車黎加佈防快？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae952154ea379b073b8f961fa0bda7b42a4ee73","tid":1386353,"uid":20908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:28:32.000Z","msg":"無人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82f9e67a30af560d29fbe421563c78a4841ea2d","tid":1386353,"uid":215505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:28:57.000Z","msg":"入室內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd85dd5168fabdcc773648910bb907a6d43150d","tid":1386353,"uid":13759,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"2ae952154ea379b073b8f961fa0bda7b42a4ee73","tid":1386353,"uid":20908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:28:32.000Z","msg":"無人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a