86353,"uid":230536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:52:59.000Z","msg":"Hit and run<br />\n轉場玩"},{"pid":"2d1ec182a18e2e64cb3a018e1a69a09f975f8eb9","tid":1386353,"uid":13759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:09:35.000Z","msg":"Hit and Run<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5aabc8dec725fb7bb3e0ce1a8e8cdd5f5c849c","tid":1386353,"uid":231413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e654dae936f31487721df94f9906dfc639a1b56","tid":1386353,"uid":13759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:24:27.000Z","msg":"講好咗Hit and Run啦，無人叫你企係度俾人射，佢黎到咪即刻散水坐車去另一區再示威過囉。<br />\n<br />\n最簡單對付警察同水炮車既方法，就係當佢要走果陣就立即走，打遊擊，諗方法對付佢做咩？打機打上腦？<br />\n<br />\n根本就無得打+無需要打。各位諗清楚我地行動目標係咩，目標就係賭香港經濟同前途去換取五大訴求！<br />\n<br />\n得罪講，你俾水炮射死政府都唔在乎，做咩要送頭？重諗點對付警察？<br />\n<br />\nBe water呀，講咗咁撚耐都唔撚係Be water。你企定定俾人射點Be Water呀！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:15:28.000Z","msg":"be 條撚water<br />\n個個一落場就當自己美隊<br />\nbe石屎就似D<br />\n等水炮車出,<br />\n仲迷戀陣地戰,<br />\n到時with water<br />\nin water<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5cb489fc8262a5c9514d451a766c95bf60c6bb","tid":1386353,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:23:41.000Z","msg":"唔好再戀戰 用啲對己方有利既策略 hit and run"},{"pid":"74ff9cf7b35e574f1719144fcaffff6a6452196d","tid":1386353,"uid":13759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12058b483b6f64e5d010aaf790824ce20cae87e","tid":1386353,"uid":13759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad88a255373f0f70897b4829d815cb0936a0c8e","tid":1386353,"uid":277345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:34:50.000Z","msg":"台灣朋友對香港人的忠告:<br />\n<br />\n給香港朋友。<br />\n<br />\n面對鎮暴水車，還沒被沖到以前你想像是加強版SPA，但其實被沖到就是像拿木棍在戳你，會內臟翻騰兩三天，沒有正面抵抗的辦法，但穿戰術背心會有緩衝效果，保護你的內臟。<br />\n<br />\n不要停留，保持距離，不要像照片一樣坐下來，但小心奔跑時被衝到，跌倒會加重受傷。盡可能全罩安全帽保護你的眼睛，水來時一定要背對，蹲馬步沒有用，水來還是倒。<br />\n<br />\n製作雞爪釘，每個游擊者在撤退的時候撒下一把又一把，拖延水車前進時間，往下一個戰場移動。<br />\n<br />\n保護你的眼睛，噴到會爆。<br />\n小心裡面裝不明液體，準備好沖洗的乾淨水源。<br />\n<br />\n祝港人平安。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mastodon.social/web/statuses/102535178775212997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmastodon.social%2Fweb%2Fstatuses%2F102535178775212997&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCufkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=f34f152b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mastodon.social/web/statuses/102535178775212997</a>"},{"pid":"2c3385c50435e7de1498c2d55c0dfc7fe3670f06","tid":1386353,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"最怕係咋邊黑警放彈封路，另一邊水炮車清場，屌黑警有乜做砳出"},{"pid":"877ff9b0dfb87c32496ee5186a8f8a1c98b1c18e","tid":1386353,"uid":279874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:38:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dec11de8d481f4c70383917c0199bc18b92947f","tid":1386353,"uid":287999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43796b5b9541b16ea9f2c2f89f973b213512a418","tid":1386353,"uid":263161,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:27:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:41:24.000Z","msg":"前題係地鐵照開，如果班狗停左地鐵就冇咁易打遊擊"},{"pid":"fc1058ff190963b03e2a5a623ea6a6ad4e16ee42","tid":1386353,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:45:43.000Z","msg":"此